According to the ''{{ill|Ruijū Sandai Kyaku|ja|類聚三代格|qq=draft|qq=draft}}'', on January 20, 808 ({{ill|Daidō|ja|大同 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} year 3), Nuribeshi was merged into the {{ill|Naishōryō|ja|内匠寮|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of the {{ill|Ministry of Central Affairs|ja|中務省|1=Ministry of the Center|lt=Nakatsukasa-shō|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.<ref>{{ill|Ruijū Sandai Kyaku|ja|類聚三代格|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Vol. 4 "Addition and Reduction of Officials and Offices," January 20, Daidō year 3.</ref>
